; Three SN76489 PSG voices: melody, counter-melody, and bass

; Melody: ascending then descending arpeggio
'B1 T140
'B1 v100 l8 o4 c e g >c < b g e c r4

; Counter-melody: offset by one beat
'B2 T140
'B2 v80 l8 o3 r4 e g b >e d b g e

; Bass: root notes on each beat
'B3 T140
'B3 v70 l4 o2 c r c r
